    "attributes": {
        "action": "Enable UK expats to have votes for life",
        "additional_details": "This was promised by David Cameron at the same time as the original Brexit referendum.\r\nMost other countries have votes-for-life, so why should UK citizens  be denied their rights to representation?\r\n\"No taxation without representation\"",
        "background": "We would like the UK to enable the British people who live abroad, to be able to vote which we feel is their right.",
